{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"4a2a98d60d","title":"关于中南军区应增加打虎预算致谭政等电","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"4db2c3e50d","index":0,"year":1952,"month":2,"day":18,"articleId":"4a2a98d60d"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji31","name":"毛泽东全集第31卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/31-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji31":{"comments":[{"id":"606b4517c1","publicationId":"maoquanji31","articleId":"4a2a98d60d","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"谭政，当时任中国人民解放军中南军区第三政治委员。2]剑英，即叶剑英，当时任中国人民解放军华南军区司令员。"},{"id":"91d5b756c5","publicationId":"maoquanji31","articleId":"4a2a98d60d","index":2,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"指谭政1952年2月13日关于目前华南军区打虎预算给毛泽东的报告。报告说，华南军区第二次预算，加上驻两广各军及广西数字，计划共捉大虎183只，中小虎2164只。"}],"contents":[{"id":"7fa9427756","type":"title","text":"关于中南军区应增加打虎预算致谭政\"等电","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji31","articleId":"4a2a98d60d"},{"id":"606b4517c1","type":"paragraph","text":"谭政同志，并告剑英","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji31","articleId":"4a2a98d60d"},{"id":"91d5b756c5","type":"paragraph","text":"二月十三日电收到。你们军区打虎预算据中南局最近电告增至打大虎八百，这比你们过去的数字是增大了，但和华东军区的一千六百相比，仅及其一半。实际上华东军区大虎将来可能打至二千五百至三千。你们基本上应与他们看齐，但可稍退一会再增加，并须启发下面同志自动增加，始不觉得太勉强。特别是华南军区系统可能打大虎一千以上，中小虎万数，而他们定得很低，勇气不旺。最近看了四十八军打虎渐多，应即以之教育全军。","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji31","articleId":"4a2a98d60d"},{"id":"aea91b16d2","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji31","articleId":"4a2a98d60d"},{"id":"e5a1d9e45d","type":"paragraph","text":"二月十八日","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji31","articleId":"4a2a98d60d"}],"page":{"id":"c3d8c07222","publicationId":"maoquanji31","articleId":"4a2a98d60d","start":411,"end":411}}}},"__N_SSG":true}